<Paragraph TextAlignment="Center" FontFamily="Cambria" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="14">OlapChart illustrating Zooming and Scrolling</Paragraph>

<BlockUIContainer>
<TextBlock Style="{DynamicResource HeaderTextStyle}">Features:</TextBlock>
</BlockUIContainer>

<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">You can achieve zooming in two ways:</Paragraph>
<List Margin="20,20,0,0">
<ListItem>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">Invoking the built-in zooming tool through the context menu by the end user.</Paragraph><Paragraph />
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">Employing the <Bold>ZoomIn</Bold> and <Bold>ZoomOut</Bold> commands when associated with the key gestures programmatically by the end user.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
</List>

